description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 1 of 3 of the live October match up between The Dragons and The Ninjas.
This is the match that we have all been waiting for. Both teams are undefeated in Tag Team Action. Both teams are powerhouses, one team has to lose and is going to get fucked and humiliated in front of a live audience.
The Ninjas are led by former championship Vendetta. Vendetta is the most decorated Wrestler in US history with more trophies than any other wrestler. Vendetta's partner this year is Tara Lynn Foxx. This sexy 20yr old is big, strong and tenacious, one of the best rookies to come out of season 7.
The Dragons are led by The Dragon. The Dragon was undefeated in regular season match play. Holly Heart is the other half of this great team, and could be one of the strongest wrestlers in the league this year.
Do not miss the two best teams mix it up. This is the best and only non-scripted live tag team wrestling anywhere in the world!
title: Two undefeated teams brutally battle it out
